<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hand-vt">hand <strong><em>vt</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /hænd/    美 /hænd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>交；递；给：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please hand me that chair. / Please hand that chair <strong>to</strong> me<strong>hand_2</strong>
请把那把椅子递给我。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="hand-around-round">hand around / round</h3>
<p>1.<strong>分发</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="hand-back">hand back</h3>
<p>1.<strong>交回；归还</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="hand-down">hand down</h3>
<p>1.<strong>把…传下来 (pass down)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This ring has been handed down in my family. 
这枚戒指是我家祖传的。</p></div>

<h3 id="hand-in">hand in</h3>
<p>1.<strong>提交；交上 (BrE give in)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If you order your lunch at the school dining hall, please hand in your order before 9:30.
如果你要在学校餐厅订午餐，请在9:30前把订单交上来。</p></div>

<h3 id="hand-out">hand out</h3>
<p>1.<strong>把…拿出来；分发 (distribute)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Every Wednesday, we work at a soup kitchen and hand out food to homeless people in the community.
每星期三，我们再施食处给社区里无家可归的人分发食物。</p><footer>人教新必修① – 1</footer></div>

<h3 id="hand-over">hand over</h3>
<p>1.<strong>移交；交出：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is certain that he will <strong>hand over</strong> his business <strong>to</strong> his son when he gets old.
当他年老时，他肯定会把生意移交给他的儿子。</p></div></div>